column4: NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "1C0A69444479124F4C611280453C2FDD", "I\'m Angemon, an angel to protect you. I\'ve awakened to fulfill my duty.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "42318B7743470D2ED34E8F9EACC33AE3", "I offer my soul to follow earthly instructions.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "F8BFE4504E02A48468A8948DA04E675F", "What\'s he talking about...? Are you coming to the city?")
NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "72C391174F836AC6C308B7A831EF1997", "Thine mission is mine duty. I go.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "8611D8CE489473C0C3C0E8A17A77C56E", "I\'m sorry, but can you speak in words I understand?")
NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "4159CDCB47F5370085FED788425E1DB2", "I\'ll go to the city, so you must keep trying.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4BC36A4D4D56B9707D4F85AE5C5AE22F]", "8611D8CE489473C0C3C0E8A17A77C56E", "I\'m sorry, but can you speak in words I understand?")
